OL,3,CBrothers praise 'phenomenal' support
OL,4,Cafter completing 33 marathons for
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FTwo brothers from Redditch in
OL,8,FWorcestershire have said they believe
OL,9,Ftheir effort has shown the "power of
OL,10,Fwhen people come together" as they
OL,11,Fcompleted 33 marathons in 33 days in
OL,12,FIreland to raise funds and awareness
OL,13,Ffor frontotemporal dementia (FTD).
OL,15,FJordan and Cian Adams carry a rare
OL,16,Fgene that causes frontotemporal
OL,17,Fdementia (FTD), which means they have
OL,18,Fa high chance of developing dementia
OL,19,Fin their 40s.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
