FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780081925
OL,3,CBrothers praise 'phenomenal' support
OL,4,Cafter completing 33 marathons for
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FTheir mother, Geraldine, died at the
OL,8,Fage of 52 after developing FTD.
OL,10,FJordan, 30, completed the 33 marathons
OL,11,Fto raise funds and awareness of
OL,12,Fdementia, with support from his physio
OL,13,Fbrother Cian, 25.
OL,15,FJordan began by running the London
OL,16,FMarathon on April 26 while carrying a
OL,17,F25kg fridge on his back, before
OL,18,Ftravelling to Ireland to run a
OL,19,Fmarathon a day in each of the 32
OL,20,Fcounties across the island.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780081925
OL,3,CBrothers praise 'phenomenal' support
OL,4,Cafter completing 33 marathons for
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FThe so-called FTD Brothers raised more
OL,8,Fthan #1 million and completed the
OL,9,Fmammoth challenge in Merrion Park
OL,10,FSquare, Dublin, where hundreds came
OL,11,Fout to support the family.
OL,13,FJordan told the crowd: "I just want to
OL,14,Fsay how much we've appreciated from
OL,15,FAntrim to Dublin, every single one of
OL,16,Fyou in your hometowns, in your
OL,17,Fcounties, come out showing your
OL,18,Fcolours, showing the real Irish
OL,19,Fspirit, and it's showing the power of
OL,20,Fwhen people come together.
OL,26,@uD@XOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780081925
OL,3,CBrothers praise 'phenomenal' support
OL,4,Cafter completing 33 marathons for
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,F"It isn't an easy time for any of us
OL,8,Fand I mean as human beings, there's a
OL,9,Flot, when you switch on the telly, to
OL,10,Fbe sad about and I hope that across
OL,11,Fthe last 33 days, we've brought hope
OL,12,Fto people not just living with
OL,13,Fdementia but we brought hope to an
OL,14,Fentire nation, because we felt your
OL,15,Fsupport every single day."
OL,17,FAs well as their mother, the brothers
OL,18,Fhave also lost an aunt to FTD, and
OL,19,FJordan said they've been on a "long,
OL,20,Flong journey as a family".
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@ZO]{D@_OU|D@YO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780081925
OL,3,CBrothers praise 'phenomenal' support
OL,4,Cafter completing 33 marathons for
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,F"I know I talk for a lot of people
OL,8,Fhere when it comes to navigating the
OL,9,Fheartbreak and devastation when it
OL,10,Fcomes to living with dementia, how
OL,11,Fisolated and unsupported, unseen,
OL,12,Funheard we feel as families," he said.
OL,14,FIn 2018, Jordan learned he was a
OL,15,Fcarrier of the gene mutation that
OL,16,Fcauses FTD.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@]O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780081925
OL,3,CBrothers praise 'phenomenal' support
OL,4,Cafter completing 33 marathons for
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FHe said: "There's no treatment,
OL,8,Fthere's no cure, and ultimately, going
OL,9,Foff the 12 relatives that I've lost to
OL,10,Fthis familial form of FTD, I will lose
OL,11,Fmy life, starting more than likely in
OL,12,Fmy mid to late 40s.
OL,14,FOver the last four weeks, thousands of
OL,15,Fpeople have come out to show their
OL,16,Fsupport for the pair, running with
OL,17,Fthem or carrying signs and cheering.
OL,26,@oD@JOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780081925
OL,3,CBrothers praise 'phenomenal' support
OL,4,Cafter completing 33 marathons for
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FSpeaking to the media after the final
OL,8,Fmarathon, Jordan said the support
OL,9,Fthey've seen "has been phenomenal, and
OL,10,Fit won't sink in for a long, long
OL,11,Ftime".
OL,13,F"It's been a special, special journey,
OL,14,Fand that's why everyone's asking me,
OL,15,F"I'm happy it's over ` not really,
OL,16,Fbecause it's been the best experience
OL,17,Fof my life to date, in terms of
OL,18,Fbringing what is a strange dream, in a
OL,19,Fsense, of making dementia visible, to
OL,20,Flight.
OL,26,@qD@NOUsD@EO]uD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780081925
OL,3,CBrothers praise 'phenomenal' support
OL,4,Cafter completing 33 marathons for
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,F"It's been something that I've been
OL,8,Fcampaigning for for eight years, and
OL,9,Fto see the amount of support here in
OL,10,FIreland, and make that happen in a
OL,11,Fplace where my mom loved so much is
OL,12,Fincredibly special."
OL,14,FCian said there had been "really tough
OL,15,Fmoments" for Jordan over the month
OL,16,Fwith "many tears shed".
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@TO]vD@ZOUwD@HO]xD@FOUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780081925
OL,3,CBrothers praise 'phenomenal' support
OL,4,Cafter completing 33 marathons for
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,F"There's been many moments,
OL,8,Fphysically, mentally, that we, you
OL,9,Fknow, might have been dubious as to
OL,10,Fwhether we were going to get him to
OL,11,FDublin but it was never really in
OL,12,Fdoubt," he said.
OL,14,FHe said the pair were "so so grateful"
OL,15,Fbut the challenge is "only the
OL,16,Fbeginning".
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@GO]vD@WOUvD@fO]wD@VOUxD@JO]
